org.apache.hadoop.fs.contract.localfs

Class LocalFSContract

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured
      • org.apache.hadoop.fs.contract.AbstractFSContract
        • org.apache.hadoop.fs.contract.localfs.LocalFSContract
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RawlocalFSContract

    public class LocalFSContract
extends AbstractFSContract
    The contract of the Local filesystem. This changes its feature set from platform for platform -the default set is updated during initialization. This contract contains some override points, to permit the raw local filesystem and other filesystems to subclass it.
